  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: e9620f8c34305754d8cc9a7e49e852d9, type: 3}
  m_Name: BossDead_en
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  m_LocaleId:
    m_Code: en
  m_SharedData: {fileID: 11400000, guid: df8f4fb56f5db9d408b7bcba5096ace8, type: 2}
  m_Metadata:
    m_Items: []
  m_TableData:
  - m_Id: 91384795136
    m_Localized: She used to be quiet and calm.... but an inperfect being changed
      her.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 94035595264
    m_Localized: And then, as she was trapped inside the frame....
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 107558031360
    m_Localized: "The clown doesn\u2019t understand what he\u2019s doing."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 109504188416
    m_Localized: "He\u2019s forgotten his situation, trapped inside the frame...
      endlessly repeating meaningless actions."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 228710502400
    m_Localized: We have to save them, Jackson...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 580298035200
    m_Localized: "You\u2019re so selfish. When you gain something, you always lose
      something else."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 582273552384
    m_Localized: "You... don\u2019t understand anything."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 583452151808
    m_Localized: "You don\u2019t even realize what\u2019s right beside you..."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 762829950976
    m_Localized: "It started as a prank \u2014 making others lose their rock to gather
      power."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 764541227008
    m_Localized: But that power... it grew beyond anything I imagined.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 765950513152
    m_Localized: I thought I had become a true king...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 767292690432
    m_Localized: But in the end, I lost all my power because of rock itself.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 768433541120
    m_Localized: Rock... truly is something extraordinary.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  references:
    version: 2
    RefIds: []
